{"tid":2429003,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人成日都會重複發同一個夢","createTime":"2021-03-02T03:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T16:51:44.000Z","uid":189222,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"06524c05506112318a9562eda42ccad30d145143","tid":2429003,"uid":189222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T03:48:01.000Z","msg":"我已經出嚟做野幾年，基本上都唔會再讀書進修<br />\n<br />\n但間中都會發夢就快要考試，我溫唔切書，或者溫溫下書瞓著咗，一醒已經就快要開考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近發呢啲夢好密，一星期會兩、三次<br />\n次次一紮醒會出晒汗，搞到個人好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前都唔為意呢啲夢，但又愈嚟愈頻密，大家又有無試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db0a8362bfcdf6844e0af3e1ed0ff20f63ee2be6","tid":2429003,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"衛斯理《尋夢》？"},{"pid":"45ecd9e878720ffbd8a4f1cf627c99b3bedadd9e","tid":2429003,"uid":7103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:23:25.000Z","msg":"壓力太大"},{"pid":"1005f0b08986040c11ee79410021f5146e0132ae","tid":2429003,"uid":318274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"發咗好多年，要重考 a level。<br />\n<br />\n每次夢入面都好真，類似知道自己原來當年考嘅成績只係 mock exam 黎，其實我未考真正嘅 a level ，之後望住 geog 本書，讀極都唔識。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀緊個時明明唔覺得 a level 咁大壓力，但咁多年都仲係發緊呢個惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410ab7fb1a236faeeecfc244f088c8c3169fcf35","tid":2429003,"uid":366281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:47:25.000Z","msg":"你去考個試會唔會就突破咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a495d30daa4b5b70aa3741030610a61bfe40d48f","tid":2429003,"uid":295652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0a8362bfcdf6844e0af3e1ed0ff20f63ee2be6","tid":2429003,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"衛斯理《尋夢》？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:53:22.000Z","msg":"好鍾意個故仔"},{"pid":"e9bf023047006d91632e3bac676d35ef0af9a407","tid":2429003,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:54:48.000Z","msg":"我就唔係完全同一個夢，但都係考試類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992744cb1709d9e4cbd76a6349815af7f20b9d75","tid":2429003,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0a8362bfcdf6844e0af3e1ed0ff20f63ee2be6","tid":2429003,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"衛斯理《尋夢》？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:57:37.000Z","msg":"電視有做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb8dc6ae42f33e228b752e58d3017d5af94092d","tid":2429003,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1005f0b08986040c11ee79410021f5146e0132ae","tid":2429003,"uid":318274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"發咗好多年，要重考 a level。<br />\n<br />\n每次夢入面都好真，類似知道自己原來當年考嘅成績只係 mock exam 黎，其實我未考真正嘅 a level ，之後望住 geog 本書，讀極都唔識。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀緊個時明明唔覺得 a level 咁大壓力，但咁多年都仲係發緊呢個惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:59:10.000Z","msg":"會唔會過後先發現其實好大壓力？一失手就好麻煩"},{"pid":"695c21f302ac413c68966806edd39f3ac9107482","tid":2429003,"uid":153609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"話時話我同樓主大致相同，<br />\n成日發夢中學孝試或中學上堂，<br />\n有時醒咗起身仲凝住返學就遲到，<br />\n其實都好撚困擾，<br />\n有冇過來人試過而又解決到？"},{"pid":"830bab05fe7bfbe9b4bcf25823abbc5a6248b904","tid":2429003,"uid":867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪因為現實中嘅我係瞞住屋企人搬咗出嚟住<br />\n我成日都發夢同佢住返<br />\n甚至係喺夢入邊為咗唔想比我屋企人知我住邊<br />\n我租多咗一個地方<br />\n成日發夢唔同房嘅格局<br />\n我一瞓醒第一下感覺都會係<br />\n嘩我邊有錢交兩間租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實發夢見到唔同嘅裝修同埋屋企又幾頂癮<br />\n不過成日都驚比屋企人發現真係幾大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969cb9f4e19cf931d2575a779ebd818fd41a5620","tid":2429003,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"992744cb1709d9e4cbd76a6349815af7f20b9d75","tid":2429003,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0a8362bfcdf6844e0af3e1ed0ff20f63ee2be6","tid":2429003,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"衛斯理《尋夢》？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:57:37.000Z","msg":"電視有做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:37:49.000Z","msg":"我睇舊版原著小說。個封面畫風勁恐怖，相得益彰"},{"pid":"f955ea49b6af9bca0228067f1a2d38b360729767","tid":2429003,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"969cb9f4e19cf931d2575a779ebd818fd41a5620","tid":2429003,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"992744cb1709d9e4cbd76a6349815af7f20b9d75","tid":2429003,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0a8362bfcdf6844e0af3e1ed0ff20f63ee2be6","tid":2429003,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"衛斯理《尋夢》？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:57:37.000Z","msg":"電視有做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:37:49.000Z","msg":"我睇舊版原著小說。個封面畫風勁恐怖，相得益彰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:40:01.000Z","msg":"羅家良嗰套個邱比特好膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09159fb99dc3e391059eaf728638441d738deee","tid":2429003,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"有啲嘢令你焦慮射箭緊張，可能連你自己都唔為意"},{"pid":"1072c5a5979b0147607709cad099757f142aece1","tid":2429003,"uid":291044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T13:57:08.000Z","msg":"細個會，夢見自己係被選中嘅勇者(唔好笑但真係好似傳統RPG)，結果永遠都係被迫犧牲自己俾舊大光球殺死然後嚇醒，最恐怖係因為已經唔係第一次發，所以夢中day 0我已經知道成個故事，有意識想改變結果但係永遠都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細佬仔嗰陣我係咪有心理疾病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20426ecc0b0e1d0bd3a5651aaeba20b2e70e2d4","tid":2429003,"uid":62482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06524c05506112318a9562eda42ccad30d145143","tid":2429003,"uid":189222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T03:48:01.000Z","msg":"我已經出嚟做野幾年，基本上都唔會再讀書進修<br />\n<br />\n但間中都會發夢就快要考試，我溫唔切書，或者溫溫下書瞓著咗，一醒已經就快要開考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近發呢啲夢好密，一星期會兩、三次<br />\n次次一紮醒會出晒汗，搞到個人好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前都唔為意呢啲夢，但又愈嚟愈頻密，大家又有無試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:46:20.000Z","msg":"係咪做嘢成日要趕deadline 好怕準備唔切?"},{"pid":"011a489aca034dbabbd9a48589c41f3ab5a853e3","tid":2429003,"uid":303298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"記得細細個發過一個夢<br />\n我屋企人係我隔離打機<br />\n然後有個勁恐怖嘅嘢行埋你斬死我<br />\n每一次企係我隔離嘅屋企人同埋行過嚟嘅嘢都唔同<br />\n一樣嘅係我永遠係俾隻嘢斬死<br />\n隔離個屋企人永遠唔會幫我<br />\n大個咗少少就冇再發呢個夢<br />\n但細個嗰時真係覺得好恐怖"},{"pid":"ffe30fea170fceaf94d3fc72e65ff0c4047c463c","tid":2429003,"uid":146089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"之前好似有，好想睇個條友個樣次次都睇唔到。"},{"pid":"14100829eba694b7cedcf687b8c2cd6fad2727c6","tid":2429003,"uid":146089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"011a489aca034dbabbd9a48589c41f3ab5a853e3","tid":2429003,"uid":303298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"記得細細個發過一個夢<br />\n我屋企人係我隔離打機<br />\n然後有個勁恐怖嘅嘢行埋你斬死我<br />\n每一次企係我隔離嘅屋企人同埋行過嚟嘅嘢都唔同<br />\n一樣嘅係我永遠係俾隻嘢斬死<br />\n隔離個屋企人永遠唔會幫我<br />\n大個咗少少就冇再發呢個夢<br />\n但細個嗰時真係覺得好恐怖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T16:45:58.000Z","msg":"屋企人都次次唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b0a17b75824184026253211173028f9360b3d4","tid":2429003,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1005f0b08986040c11ee79410021f5146e0132ae","tid":2429003,"uid":318274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"發咗好多年，要重考 a level。<br />\n<br />\n每次夢入面都好真，類似知道自己原來當年考嘅成績只係 mock exam 黎，其實我未考真正嘅 a level ，之後望住 geog 本書，讀極都唔識。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀緊個時明明唔覺得 a level 咁大壓力，但咁多年都仲係發緊呢個惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T16:48:19.000Z","msg":"我AL之後。有10年，都耐唔耐發夢就嚟考文化篇章份卷，但我未溫過。直頭係唔知內文係乜，然後去考<br />\n<br />\n現實，我當年真係唔知依份卷想點，最驚係依份，結果真係F<br />\n<br />\n到幾年我把心一橫，上網搵返嗰6篇文嚟睇，睇左一次，知道返佢up乜9，就好似完左心願咁，冇再發依個夢了"},{"pid":"5d2d925ea568f2c271d585933c1d853925cf06fd","tid":2429003,"uid":146089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffe30fea170fceaf94d3fc72e65ff0c4047c463c","tid":2429003,"uid":146089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T16:43:27.000Z","msg":"之前好似有，好想睇個條友個樣次次都睇唔到。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"詳細小小<br />\n係一個純白環境，有條友長頭髮永遠係背面，我係好想睇佢咩樣。<br />\n不過之後就冇發拉，最刺激係跳樓，個身體有free fall 反應 抽一抽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家想發都冇拉。"}]}